---
import MainLayout from "../../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Transform Program | Personal Training">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Transform</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Physical transformation programs to help you achieve your fitness goals.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Our Transform programs are designed to help you achieve significant physical changes through expert guidance, personalized training, and nutritional support. Whether you want to lose fat, gain muscle, or completely transform your physique, we have a program for you.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Our Transform Programs</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-4">
        <a href="/wellness/personal-training/transform/fat-loss" class="card p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Fat Loss</h3>
          <p>Specialized program to help you burn fat and improve body composition.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/wellness/personal-training/transform/muscle-gain" class="card p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Muscle Gain</h3>
          <p>Focused training to build strength, size, and definition.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
